{"tid":1695180,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"危疾儲蓄有無需要買","createTime":"2019-11-05T13:16:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T14:10:09.000Z","uid":141597,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f483e1018549c430bd033a0a80f402f6c6f9a742","tid":1695180,"uid":141597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:16:51.000Z","msg":"廿零歲<br />\n屋企有病史 cancer，父母其中一邊<br />\n<br />\n本身有高端醫療同無儲蓄危疾，應唔應該轉少少無儲蓄去有儲蓄保終身"},{"pid":"3532104b0ec6bad8b8a8661c003e70beaa9662d9","tid":1695180,"uid":141597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:17:50.000Z","msg":"但好多都話危疾有儲蓄好搵笨"},{"pid":"1462f94fd94955d4c1fb3703d8c96d7ee27c989d","tid":1695180,"uid":141597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:38:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6795da846cd1bbc46f037e2e37755fc5861fb38f","tid":1695180,"uid":236653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3532104b0ec6bad8b8a8661c003e70beaa9662d9","tid":1695180,"uid":141597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:17:50.000Z","msg":"但好多都話危疾有儲蓄好搵笨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:54:58.000Z","msg":"儲蓄危疾 多數包埋多重保障(&gt;100%, 一生人中幾次) 早期保障(eg通波仔) 糖尿病併發 跟住又有埋人壽(100%) 兼保到99/100歲 非保證紅利 <strong>所以貴啲</strong><br />\n<br />\n話搵笨係因為抱住要食到盡個保額 又唔想俾1蚊agent/保險公司賺<br />\n<br />\n例如個plan保到1000% 啲人覺得要中十次危疾贏返保險公司先無搵笨<br />\n<br />\n呢啲係對保險價值觀既問題 唔係儲唔儲蓄危疾既原因 甚至其他保險計劃都可以話搵笨 但係百貨賣百客<br />\n<br />\neg 非agent，自己都有買儲蓄危疾"},{"pid":"039f1d8a9b52c70fd2e8f64c0f19e65115259103","tid":1695180,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:14:53.000Z","msg":"危疾有儲蓄<br />\n但唔會睇儲蓄果部份<br />\n主要供個大額保障<br />\n自己覺得值唔值得就見仁見智<br />\n <br />\nAia 做全保理財分析 有興趣搵我可以了解下<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ultramaticdiamond\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fultramaticdiamond&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=0e566d16\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ultramaticdiamond</a>"},{"pid":"2063238bc82a011a44259b737d93fd2d4bfa8d7e","tid":1695180,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3532104b0ec6bad8b8a8661c003e70beaa9662d9","tid":1695180,"uid":141597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:17:50.000Z","msg":"但好多都話危疾有儲蓄好搵笨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:18:20.000Z","msg":"你要賺錢嘅話就乜嘢都係搵笨，你要保障嘅話就冇得講， 你有幾千萬現金嘅咪唔使買，你全家等你養嘅咁有個保障都好，depends on你嘅負擔<br />\n我自己有買嘅，以我所知我朋友響保監局度做精算師，佢都有買危疾"},{"pid":"6e61dc1719e92db663d3a0bf738246a9a6524ca7","tid":1695180,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:18:52.000Z","msg":"無儲蓄危疾&gt;有儲蓄危疾<br />\n儲蓄自己儲"},{"pid":"81239fa09aa02b66dad6e04def3497337d97e0a1","tid":1695180,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:19:12.000Z","msg":"有儲蓄當你有一日供完舊錢係拎得返<br />\n（當然唔係要你供曬個額）<br />\n當中都只係做一個槓桿<br />\n如果唔係你就要買終生條數襟計<br />\n冇儲蓄成份嘅通常只會保到一個年期 <br />\n有儲蓄成份同埋當你一中咗招份嘢唔使再供<br />\n仍然會保多你幾次 跟一世"},{"pid":"a184c3c4f9526e76c643d85f022d9c44f99e32bb","tid":1695180,"uid":7353,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:21:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed7d30fd2f5f52acce281717d1512e2a5fb426a6","tid":1695180,"uid":149779,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:29:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f795be95aac00fcd48c2292b0d5d510b5079d4c","tid":1695180,"uid":141597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T16:08:01.000Z","msg":"但而家sell緊我嗰份無得拎返錢走，月供成千供廿幾年好似有啲喇脷"},{"pid":"e904af6206ffd5d7f94fdab96232200f02114d40","tid":1695180,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T16:38:01.000Z","msg":"唔識既話 見到儲蓄2個字一律唔買"},{"pid":"aa416aadfe5360e81af6ed00fe157a5556997362","tid":1695180,"uid":236653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f795be95aac00fcd48c2292b0d5d510b5079d4c","tid":1695180,"uid":141597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T16:08:01.000Z","msg":"但而家sell緊我嗰份無得拎返錢走，月供成千供廿幾年好似有啲喇脷"},"cit